Date of Birth: December 2, 1886<br/>
Birthplace: Taylorsville, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: April 9, 1953<br/>
Death: February. 11, 1958<br/>
<br/>
Born Dec. 2, 1886, at Taylorsville, Salt Lake Co., Utah, to Joseph Bennion and Mary A. Sharp. Ordained apostle April 9, 1953, by David 0. McKay, at age 66; died Feb. 11, 1958, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at 71.